<div align="justify">there are moments when i wake up and i forget that i will not find you sleeping next to me. i'm such a child, clinging to love when it's kicked me to the dirt so many times. 

we try.

clementine: i wish you'd stayed. 
joel: i wish I'd stayed, too. NOW i wish i'd stayed.  i wish i'd done a lot of things. i wish i'd... i wish i'd stayed... i do.
75% friend only. friends only, darlings.
